Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:03.70,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,3600)\bord2.25\3c&H1F1F1F&\be6\c&HFFFFFC&}so ra no wo to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.85,0:00:13.52,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}The brilliant glow of this sky, does it carry right into your heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.83,0:00:22.91,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,1600)\3c&H141414&}The melody you heard in your dream, it plays like the silence
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.53,0:00:28.12,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Even if your hands are still far from that dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.12,0:00:33.34,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Come now and remember that kindly voice
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.34,0:00:46.28,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(50,200)\3c&H141414&}Someone was there singing for you, the happiness they sang about
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.28,0:00:55.68,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Sound of the sky, echo on high, break through that overwhelming sadness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.68,0:01:00.62,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Everything that shines in your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.62,0:01:06.08,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,400)\3c&H141414&}Is part of the real world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.34,0:01:15.55,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(100,200)\3c&H141414&}Even your tears can't leave you here to stay forever
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.71,0:01:27.51,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,4000)\3c&H141414&}In this gentle light pouring down onto you, play tomorrow's song
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.51,0:02:02.51,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&00&}One Typhoon Passes - What You Really See
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.36,0:22:46.43,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Love and friendship - put these feelings together
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.43,0:22:49.22,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}And sing of how important they are
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.57,0:23:07.70,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I was so happy that I cried
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.54,0:23:13.67,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}It hurt so bad that I laughed
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.50,0:23:22.51,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}But that all just goes to show that I'm alive
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.51,0:23:26.64,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,800)}Let's just walk it slowly
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.64,0:23:28.33,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HE5A9EA&}Everybody singing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.33,0:23:32.62,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Just tell me a bit of what you think
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.62,0:23:33.94,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HE5A9EA&}You're just my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.94,0:23:39.95,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Love and friendship - even though they might waver
Dialogue: 1,0:23:36.98,0:23:39.95,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HE5A9EA&\an8}I know, you know, little happy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.95,0:23:45.78,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I want us to echo on forever
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.69,0:23:45.78,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HE5A9EA&\an8}Can you hear my precious note?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.78,0:23:52.16,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}All these words that there are can't even describe it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.16,0:23:57.91,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,1400)}Our harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.91,0:24:02.55,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,1400)}Can you hear it? Our harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.83,0:01:43.04,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.66,0:01:57.51,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure feels like fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.51,0:02:06.90,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so your dad was a tankman?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.90,0:02:12.23,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. He was part of the platoon that led over a thousand civilians and soldiers out of Wardenburg when it was under siege
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.23,0:02:15.66,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,with just six Type-2 Millipads.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.40,0:02:19.66,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A legendary hero during that legendary escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.91,0:02:22.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.13,0:02:23.16,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.16,0:02:31.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And after he received a life-threatening injury in battle, he met my mother who was an orderly at the hospital he was sent to!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.18,0:02:33.98,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And you were born out of their love,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.92,0:02:36.83,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,right, Kureha?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.83,0:02:38.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.86,0:02:41.99,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I look like a potato to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.99,0:02:45.31,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,My, what a wonderful potato she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.31,0:02:48.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You raised them very well, Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.55,0:02:54.69,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We can probably give some to the people in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.69,0:02:58.46,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And Klaus should be coming soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.46,0:03:00.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we give some to him as a gift?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.70,0:03:02.49,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he really coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.49,0:03:06.07,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You really love Klaus, don't you Kureha?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.07,0:03:08.75,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that I like him,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.75,0:03:10.60,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I just have a lot of respect for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.62,0:03:33.86,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.86,0:03:37.47,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! She can even play it like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.47,0:03:39.65,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my Rio!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.65,0:03:40.86,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.07,0:03:51.87,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The wind is starting to pick up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.56,0:03:55.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The weather might be taking a bad turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.79,0:03:57.63,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we stop here for today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.63,0:03:58.33,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.33,0:03:59.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.15,0:04:00.74,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël, you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.89,0:04:14.62,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.62,0:04:16.85,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think Rio's been acting strange lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.85,0:04:17.90,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What part?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.90,0:04:20.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Like her trumpet-playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.15,0:04:22.45,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it wonderful? It's so smooth!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.45,0:04:24.95,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Like she's feeling blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.95,0:04:27.78,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She never did like making small talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.78,0:04:30.42,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But... Right! Dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.42,0:04:32.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't that {\i1}tempura{\i0} delicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.79,0:04:35.61,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! The potatoes were so steamy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.61,0:04:36.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, not that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.80,0:04:44.67,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you are, Rio. Eat it while it's hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.67,0:04:45.88,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.88,0:04:47.23,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.49,0:04:51.70,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.70,0:04:52.72,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.72,0:04:54.89,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.87,0:04:59.07,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Bell peppers!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.07,0:05:01.32,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She was practically wolfing them down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.82,0:05:03.45,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio ate them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.45,0:05:04.23,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.23,0:05:09.49,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how finely you chop them, she seeks, finds, and removes every last piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.49,0:05:11.23,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio ate them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.23,0:05:14.58,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That... might mean something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.90,0:05:29.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.35,0:05:36.53,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this Klaus?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.53,0:05:38.45,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! It's my treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.45,0:05:41.45,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The Desert Wolf, Miracle Klaus!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.45,0:05:46.25,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,On his left breast, he has a tattoo of the insignia of Platoon 481,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.25,0:05:48.04,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,the glorious Wolf Head!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.04,0:05:51.78,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't he look amazing? You can't have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.97,0:05:57.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you have to worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.61,0:06:02.55,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,When the Commander looked down, it was just us worrying, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.42,0:06:06.74,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.74,0:06:08.49,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We're talking about Rio,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.49,0:06:11.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,the cool, stylish, and beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.44,0:06:12.84,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.84,0:06:17.54,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she just got over her fear of bell peppers and ate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.54,0:06:21.56,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You really love Rio, don't you Kureha?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.56,0:06:24.78,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always admired her, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.78,0:06:27.37,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I admire her too, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.37,0:06:29.45,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Noël?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.83,0:06:38.83,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.24,0:06:52.23,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for Noël to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.23,0:06:56.40,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no helping her. I'll lend her half of my bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.40,0:06:58.72,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata, take that side.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.72,0:07:00.23,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.37,0:07:18.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The fire for the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.13,0:07:19.90,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You forgot to put it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.90,0:07:22.58,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I forgot all about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.22,0:07:28.14,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Looking like you've got everything under control and forgetting one thing is the best part about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.14,0:07:30.74,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But you've been forgetting too many things lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.74,0:07:32.45,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.45,0:07:38.14,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you regretting hanging up on your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.65,0:07:44.72,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't do anything about it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.72,0:07:48.03,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll cover whatever mistakes you make.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.78,0:07:55.73,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,At least try to be be a cool mentor in front of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.84,0:08:02.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it the wind?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.17,0:08:05.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't sound like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.41,0:08:09.31,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to come in the middle of the night. Class-one priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.31,0:08:10.76,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it addressed to?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.76,0:08:15.34,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Platoon 1121. Master Sergeant Rio Kazumiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.03,0:08:20.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Get the receipt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.87,0:08:31.38,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Major, please come inside for the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.38,0:08:34.71,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be going anywhere in this weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.71,0:08:36.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you're the Desert Wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.57,0:08:39.93,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to call me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.93,0:08:41.08,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.08,0:08:45.58,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,How about some hot tea and a bath as an apology?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.54,0:08:53.09,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We appreciate your diligence in completing your mission in this typhoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.09,0:08:59.10,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry we only have leftovers from last night, but please do eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.68,0:09:06.86,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You should have woken me up when Klaus got here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.69,0:09:14.47,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,These are good! Delicious even after it's cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.47,0:09:16.51,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The bell peppers were raised very well too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.51,0:09:17.98,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.98,0:09:21.33,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I picked them, and I fried them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.37,0:09:25.23,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll make a good wife someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.33,0:09:28.72,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the latest newspaper?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.72,0:09:32.75,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. The Major brought it here for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.75,0:09:34.54,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The peace treaty?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.54,0:09:37.65,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like the conferences still aren't going smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.65,0:09:40.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Neither side is making any compromises.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.01,0:09:45.39,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Things would be completely different if Princess Iliya were still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.41,0:09:47.80,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.49,0:09:49.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Iliya?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.70,0:09:53.95,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you can't not know who she is! The Hero of Binnenland!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.95,0:09:57.62,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The first daughter of Archduke Arkadia!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.62,0:10:00.32,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The Goddess of Victory of the Helvetian Army,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.32,0:10:04.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,a tankman as legendary as the Desert Wolf, Major Klaus!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.79,0:10:07.87,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.36,0:10:09.72,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You all here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.72,0:10:11.38,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got an emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.16,0:10:29.37,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio! Rio!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.94,0:10:40.94,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What's all the ruckus?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.94,0:10:44.42,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,One of the kids at Yumina's church hasn't been seen since morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.42,0:10:45.90,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Help us out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.90,0:10:46.73,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.73,0:10:48.41,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sister Yumina, who went missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.20,0:10:53.93,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Seiya...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.93,0:10:58.93,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\an3\pos(1840,1050)}Sound of the Sky
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.93,0:11:03.93,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\an1\pos(80,1050)}Sound of the Sky
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.72,0:11:08.90,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The river's water has risen quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.90,0:11:12.72,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The fields downstream haven't been harvested yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.72,0:11:15.07,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If the dam breaks, they're all gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.07,0:11:17.59,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not familiar with the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.59,0:11:18.82,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Show me the way, Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.82,0:11:20.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.11,0:11:23.16,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I am so very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.16,0:11:26.04,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I only took my eyes off him for a second...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.04,0:11:29.16,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Search and rescue is part of our duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.16,0:11:30.54,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.17,0:11:38.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.01,0:11:39.05,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.05,0:11:45.39,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Seiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.39,0:11:46.81,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Seiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.54,0:11:57.03,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.03,0:11:58.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The water is so rough...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.06,0:12:01.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If he fell in there...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.20,0:12:09.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Seiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.71,0:12:11.12,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Seiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.80,0:12:18.06,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.06,0:12:19.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.51,0:12:23.76,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You know something, don't you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.50,0:12:27.05,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You came out here because you know where he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.76,0:12:30.64,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me! Where is Seiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.98,0:12:35.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The field.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.15,0:12:36.60,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Field?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.60,0:12:37.62,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Eggplants.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.62,0:12:39.90,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They're Sister Yumina's favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.90,0:12:45.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So we all saved our allowances to buy seeds...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.28,0:12:46.41,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Seiya...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.79,0:12:50.25,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you plant them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.52,0:13:16.40,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.40,0:13:19.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,In a place like this in the middle of a typhoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.44,0:13:21.14,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm protecting these eggplants!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.14,0:13:23.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you thinking? Don't you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.97,0:13:25.82,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We're risking our lives for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.82,0:13:29.20,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You decided to come here yourself! No one asked for your help!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.20,0:13:31.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.70,0:13:33.37,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough out of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.96,0:13:45.40,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up. Kids without parents have to think harder than other kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.40,0:13:49.08,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If you cause trouble for people, you know who they'll blame?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.49,0:13:52.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.44,0:13:53.80,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yumina.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.54,0:13:56.85,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll go after your Sister too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.85,0:13:58.86,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.24,0:14:05.74,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an orphan too. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.74,0:14:09.24,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then. Let's head back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.24,0:14:10.83,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.83,0:14:13.14,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And you still feel like whining?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.14,0:14:15.26,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.26,0:14:22.34,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You come to value things that you raise from nothing as much as your own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.84,0:14:28.14,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Once eggplants are this big, you can eat them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.09,0:14:32.93,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll taste amazing if you pickle them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.05,0:14:38.19,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.19,0:14:40.69,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Major?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.85,0:14:52.65,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Seiya has started climbing back up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.54,0:15:05.77,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Major, go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.10,0:15:15.60,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,N- No. You go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.60,0:15:17.73,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take up the rear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.39,0:15:19.35,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.68,0:15:51.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They're both safe. Thank goodness. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.30,0:15:54.55,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Now there's no way for them to climb back up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.55,0:15:58.31,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The situation... is grim.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.32,0:16:07.54,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.38,0:16:10.82,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The situation has gotten worse,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.82,0:16:14.32,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,but you're here, Major.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.28,0:16:18.33,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you'll find a way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.82,0:16:22.08,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.08,0:16:24.71,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.54,0:16:26.81,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.91,0:16:33.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up. No need to fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.18,0:16:36.72,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, Miracle Klaus is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.72,0:16:37.93,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.90,0:16:40.73,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The ground is starting to collapse.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.73,0:16:43.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The water's breaking down the soil...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.01,0:16:46.23,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! This is why I hate kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.23,0:16:51.49,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kids who can't listen should just be tied up and locked in a dark room!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.49,0:16:52.11,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.24,0:16:55.24,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing will come from panicking!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.48,0:17:00.20,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Those three are always watching you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.49,0:17:04.50,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry... I went too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.50,0:17:08.04,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,B- But they'll figure something out, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.04,0:17:10.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They call Klaus a miracle worker, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.70,0:17:11.88,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.26,0:17:18.14,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,He isn't the Desert Wolf or Miracle Klaus.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.14,0:17:23.07,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They just happened to have the same name and look similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.18,0:17:28.40,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,When they first met, Kureha got excited and decided he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.40,0:17:30.65,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You know how Klaus is bad with words.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.65,0:17:34.40,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,He never found a way to tell her, and so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.40,0:17:36.53,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.53,0:17:41.29,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we have to find a way to rescue a courier
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.29,0:17:44.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,with only a long service history and an aspiring soldier
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.97,0:17:48.16,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,without a shred of experience from that ledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.16,0:17:50.55,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Throw them a rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.64,0:17:53.30,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't any anchors above them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.30,0:17:57.80,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They're too far away to throw a rope from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.80,0:18:01.93,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If there were a way to throw a rope over there...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.78,0:18:03.81,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.28,0:18:08.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,When I first met you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.44,0:18:13.49,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that maybe if my father were still alive, he would be like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.49,0:18:19.81,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I tell people about him like I knew him well,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.81,0:18:23.29,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,but I actually heard it all from other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.29,0:18:25.48,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really know much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.48,0:18:29.49,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,He died before I understood anything at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.49,0:18:30.80,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.75,0:18:58.86,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Left... At attention, signal?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.81,0:19:02.37,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The Takemicaduchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.37,0:19:08.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Halt!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.88,0:19:13.88,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it, Noël?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.88,0:19:17.10,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Anchor-use linear coil now operational.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.10,0:19:21.62,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Targeting system, E-7 to F-5 activated.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.62,0:19:22.76,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Initializing targeting system.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.02,0:19:31.27,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.27,0:19:34.27,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Wire anchor, standby to fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.27,0:19:35.78,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata, do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.78,0:19:36.78,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.83,0:19:47.91,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.29,0:19:54.48,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect you just like your father would if he were alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.80,0:19:58.06,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.78,0:20:00.05,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Major.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.47,0:20:04.55,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Standby! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.05,0:20:12.10,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.82,0:20:15.62,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.62,0:20:16.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Major!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.55,0:20:26.12,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.12,0:20:28.08,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Reel in the anchor! Full speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.82,0:20:59.07,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Kureha...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.07,0:21:03.07,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you now that we made it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.07,0:21:03.96,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.96,0:21:05.95,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You're exactly what I thought you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.24,0:21:09.54,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The man I admire most.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.77,0:21:27.03,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The blue sky after a typhoon passes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.03,0:21:28.88,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So you played the part the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.88,0:21:30.74,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Frankly, I'm surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.74,0:21:33.06,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Never thought you had it in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.06,0:21:40.64,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,When I looked into those eyes, shattering Kureha's dreams frightened me more than death. She believed in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.64,0:21:44.39,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's probably how I managed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.53,0:21:48.96,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, I'm just a coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.96,0:21:52.51,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true at all! You were wonderful, Klaus!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.91,0:21:55.58,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.58,0:22:02.84,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What someone watching sees and what the person front and center feels are completely different things.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.84,0:22:07.91,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The lenses we call admiration are always out of focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.91,0:22:10.60,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, someone will see you through those lenses.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.60,0:22:13.03,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll know how it feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.03,0:22:17.82,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you at least stay until Kureha wakes up?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.82,0:22:20.11,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Mind telling Kureha something for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.11,0:22:26.66,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This baby's the best life-threatening injury I've ever had!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.52,0:24:13.73,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(960,405)\c&H020202&\bord0}Next time: Departure - When the First Snow Falls
